name: Oversized "Lies Are Free, Talk Is Cheap" Shirt
description:
Everyone likes to be sassy, bossy, and tell a few lies once in awhile. Make a statement in this black oversized American Apparel shirt that features a large skull and the phrase "Lies Are Free, Talk Is Cheap" in an elegant but edgy font.

This shirt is made to have a larger fit and hang lower in the front or off one shoulder. The material is very light, thin, and is normally worn over tank tops. 

It only comes in two sizes, Small/Medium (+1) & Large/XL (+2)
Depending on your size or how baggy you want the shirt is the way you order.

Printed on a Black AA Viscose Shirt. with White font.
This shirt is 100% Viscose.

Available in +1 (Small/Medium) & +2 (Large/XLarge)

name: I Am Rock n' Roll T-Shirt
description:
Printed on a charcoal gray short sleeved t-shirt, this statement piece proves that you are edgy, powerful, and live the music known as Rock n' Roll. Become the center of attention and have all eyes looking your way with the sharp glossy red ink and bold star that are featured in the design.

Charcoal Gildan T-shirt with Black & fire engine red letters.
The shirt is 100% Cotton.

Available in Small, & Medium.

SOLD OUT IN L & XL.

name: "Real Love Lasts Forever" V-Neck
description:
Everyone has a soul mate and when they find that person it is real, perfect, and lasts forever. It is a relationship full of spark, romance, and love. A relationship that goes through hard times, sad times, and amazing times but no matter what, will fight through it until the end. It doesn't last a week, a month, a year, it lasts forever.

This shirt was inspired by a couple that have a real love that will last forever. It was made as a reminder to them, you, and I that you will find that certain someone who you will spend the rest of your life with, some people just find them sooner than others.

Let everyone know that you believe in real love while wearing this AA heather gray v-neck featuring a black handwriting font and scribbled heart.

Printed on a Heather Gray American Apparel V-Neck with black font.
This shirt is 90% combed cotton & 10% Polyester.

Available in Small & Medium

SOLD OUT IN SMALL, LARGE & XLARGE
